    "patch_code": "private void updateBounds(TimePeriod period, int index) {\n    \n    long start = period.getStart().getTime();\n    long end = period.getEnd().getTime();\n    long middle = start + ((end - start) / 2);\n\n    updateBound(this.minStartIndex, start, index);\n    updateBound(this.maxStartIndex, start, index);\n    \n    updateBound(this.minMiddleIndex, middle, index);\n    updateBound(this.maxMiddleIndex, middle, index);\n        \n    updateBound(this.minEndIndex, end, index);\n    updateBound(this.maxEndIndex, end, index);         \n}\n\npublic void updateBound(int currentIndex, long value, int index){\n    if (currentIndex < 0){\n        this.minStartIndex = index;  \n        return;\n    }      \n     \n    TimePeriod currentPeriod =  getDataItem(currentIndex).getPeriod();\n    long compareValue = currentPeriod.getStart().getTime();\n    \n    if (value < compareValue ){\n        this.minStartIndex = index;  \n    }else if(value > compareValue){\n        this.maxStartIndex = index;  \n    } \n }",
