    "patch_code": "private void updateBounds(TimePeriod period, int index) {\n    \n    long start = period.getStart().getTime();\n    long end = period.getEnd().getTime();\n    long middle = start + ((end - start) / 2);\n\n    updateMinOrMax(this.minStartIndex, start, index);\n    updateMinOrMax(this.maxStartIndex, start, index);\n    updateMinOrMax(this.minMiddleIndex, middle, index);\n    updateMinOrMax(this.maxMiddleIndex, middle, index);\n    updateMinOrMax(this.minEndIndex, end, index);\n    updateMinOrMax(this.maxEndIndex, end, index);\n}\n\nprivate void updateMinOrMax(int currentIndex, long value, int newIndex) {\n    if (currentIndex >= 0) {\n       TimePeriod period =  getDataItem(currentIndex).getPeriod();        \n       long storedValue = period.getStart().getTime();\n       if ((value < storedValue && currentIndex != newIndex) ||\n           (value == storedValue && currentIndex > newIndex)) {\n          return;\n       }\n    }\n    currentIndex = newIndex;\n}",
